citeinfo.title: Senate District Boundaries, Minnesota, 2012

descript.abstract: This is a polygon data set of the 2012 Senate District Boundaries. It displays county names and district numbers with associated members. It was derived from U.S. Census Bureau 2010 TIGER/Line files as a result of 2010 redistricting efforts.
descript.purpose: This data was created to display current Senate District boundaries and to allow geographical review/analysis adhereing to MN Senate District boundaries.

browse.browsed: Statewide view of Senate District Boundaries

timeperd.current: This file is current as of 2010 Census Bureau redistricting efforts. Boundary updates are completed every decennial census.

procstep.procdesc: This database of Senate District Boundaries was developed from U.S. Census Bureau 2010 TIGER/Line files. The redistricting boundaries were extracted from the 2010 TIGER/Line files using Maptitude software. Manual editing was completed to add attribute field containing district member and party affliation

attracc.attraccr: Attributes represent information regarding district member

overview.eaover: "MNSENDIST" - Senate District number "name" - Senator Name "Party" - Political Party
